      • SmartCardLoginInfo

        public SmartCardLoginInfo(byte[] certArray)
                   throws TeamRepositoryException
        This constructor takes an X.509 certificate as a DER-encoded byte array and finds the alias of the corresponding certificate in the KeyStore if it exists . This alias will be set as the alias to use when authenticating with the server.
        Parameters:
        certArray - The DER-encoded representation of an X.509 certificate to identify the login certificate
        Throws:
        TeamRepositoryException
